organization.title: Leasehold Advisory Service
organization.description:
The Leasehold Advisory Service (LEASE) gives free legal advice to leaseholders, landlords, professional advisers, managers and others on the law affecting residential leasehold in England and Wales.

LEASE is an executive non-departmental public body of the Department for Communities and Local Government

http://www.lease-advice.org/
